adviseScripts.text: Hey, Sweetie.
adviseScripts.speaker: Rupee

adviseScripts.text: The last day of the year is the most special day of the year.
adviseScripts.speaker: Rupee

adviseScripts.text: What's a good way to ring in the New Year?
adviseScripts.speaker: Rupee

adviseScripts.text: Going on a date with your loved one.
Participating in a massive gaming event.
That does sound nice.
adviseScripts.speaker: Rupee

adviseScripts.text: Then... check out this!
adviseScripts.speaker: Rupee

adviseScripts.text: "Top 10 Dating Hotspots to Ring in the New Year". You can choose one from this list... but two would be even better!
adviseScripts.speaker: Rupee

adviseScripts.text: Interesting...
adviseScripts.speaker: Rupee

adviseScripts.text: Any chance I could join?
adviseScripts.speaker: Rupee

adviseScripts.text: I have a conversation about end-of-the-year plans with Rupee.
Sweetie, come over here. Let's take a photo together.
adviseScripts.speaker: Rupee

adviseScripts.text: One, two...
adviseScripts.speaker: Rupee

adviseScripts.text: Nikke!
Shut eyes.
*Click*
Let's see how it turned out.
adviseScripts.speaker: Rupee

adviseScripts.text: *Gasp* You're not gonna believe this Sweetie, but...
adviseScripts.speaker: Rupee

adviseScripts.text: I think I just took an all-time greatest photo of us!
adviseScripts.speaker: Rupee

adviseScripts.text: *Click*
Let's see how it turned out.
adviseScripts.speaker: Rupee

adviseScripts.text: Do you not like taking photos with me or something?
adviseScripts.speaker: Rupee

adviseScripts.text: I spend time editing photos with Rupee.
Helloooo! My lovely Lupins.
adviseScripts.speaker: Rupee

adviseScripts.text: A lot of people have been curious about what Commander Sweetie and I do on an average day,
adviseScripts.speaker: Rupee

adviseScripts.text: so for this video,
adviseScripts.speaker: Rupee

adviseScripts.text: I'll be preparing a special vlog recording our advising session.
adviseScripts.speaker: Rupee

adviseScripts.text: I'll hand it over to Sweetie to explain the rest.
adviseScripts.speaker: Rupee

adviseScripts.text: Talk about the importance of Nikkes and their mental health.
Explain how this is mainly where you give Nikkes their salary, and not much else.
So professional, am I right everyone?
adviseScripts.speaker: Rupee

adviseScripts.text: If it weren't for these sessions, we Nikkes might not have the courage to keep fighting.
adviseScripts.speaker: Rupee

adviseScripts.text: Sweetie! We're live right now!
adviseScripts.speaker: Rupee

adviseScripts.text: What are your superiors going to think when they see this?
adviseScripts.speaker: Rupee

adviseScripts.text: I help Rupee make a vlog about our advising session.
Anne looks just like a fairy, doesn't she?
adviseScripts.speaker: Rupee

adviseScripts.text: Sometimes I think about how nice it'd be if I were like that.
adviseScripts.speaker: Rupee

adviseScripts.text: Everyone is uniquely charming in their own way.
I like you just the way you are.
I know...
adviseScripts.speaker: Rupee

adviseScripts.text: It was just a random thought, that's all. Hehe.
adviseScripts.speaker: Rupee

adviseScripts.text: You're making me emotional...
adviseScripts.speaker: Rupee

adviseScripts.text: You're... you're the best thing that's ever happened to me.
adviseScripts.speaker: Rupee

adviseScripts.text: I discuss with Rupee about Anne's cuteness.
I'm a little concerned our new winter accessories are underperforming.
adviseScripts.speaker: Rupee

adviseScripts.text: Is there any way we can promote them better?
adviseScripts.speaker: Rupee

adviseScripts.text: Wear them in your next video.
Increase the marketing budget.
*Gasp*
adviseScripts.speaker: Rupee

adviseScripts.text: I'm such an idiot! Why didn't I think of that?
adviseScripts.speaker: Rupee

adviseScripts.text: Here I was considering spending money to hire a model.
adviseScripts.speaker: Rupee

adviseScripts.text: Hmm...
adviseScripts.speaker: Rupee

adviseScripts.text: To tell you the truth, I've been putting a bigger focus on clothing this winter than accessories.
adviseScripts.speaker: Rupee

adviseScripts.text: I don't have much money to spare on the marketing side of things.
adviseScripts.speaker: Rupee

adviseScripts.text: Both of us think hard about ways to promote the new winter accessories.
'Tis the season, and you know what that means? Shopping!
adviseScripts.speaker: Rupee

adviseScripts.text: How about we go shopping when we're done talking?
adviseScripts.speaker: Rupee

adviseScripts.text: On a cold day like this, you ought to stay indoors.
Sure, we can buy some winter clothes.
Good point.
adviseScripts.speaker: Rupee

adviseScripts.text: So what you're saying is...
adviseScripts.speaker: Rupee

adviseScripts.text: we should stay inside and shop online?
adviseScripts.speaker: Rupee

adviseScripts.text: You'd look great in the newest fashions!
adviseScripts.speaker: Rupee

adviseScripts.text: I can see it now... you covered head to toe in the latest winter fashions.
adviseScripts.speaker: Rupee

adviseScripts.text: You'll look so cool!
adviseScripts.speaker: Rupee

adviseScripts.text: Rupee and I discuss our winter shopping plans.
I want to buy some Christmas ornaments,
adviseScripts.speaker: Rupee

adviseScripts.text: but I already bought so many. There's barely enough room left on the tree.
adviseScripts.speaker: Rupee

adviseScripts.text: Sounds like you have to swap out some of the ornaments.
Then let's buy another tree.
I can't do that!
adviseScripts.speaker: Rupee

adviseScripts.text: I love each and every last one of my decorations!
adviseScripts.speaker: Rupee

adviseScripts.text: I don't know. I'll keep thinking and see if I come up with something.
adviseScripts.speaker: Rupee

adviseScripts.text: That's genius!
adviseScripts.speaker: Rupee

adviseScripts.text: Your IQ must be like... 500 or something.
adviseScripts.speaker: Rupee

adviseScripts.text: I look around for Christmas ornaments with Rupee in the online shopping mall.
Whenever I'm outside and hear people singing Christmas songs,
adviseScripts.speaker: Rupee

adviseScripts.text: I always end up thinking of a special someone.
adviseScripts.speaker: Rupee

adviseScripts.text: Who's that?
I'm the same way.
You're awfully slow sometimes, Sweetie.
adviseScripts.speaker: Rupee

adviseScripts.text: Oh, really? Who do you think of?
adviseScripts.speaker: Rupee

adviseScripts.text: It's not... me, by any chance, is it?
adviseScripts.speaker: Rupee

adviseScripts.text: I have a conversation with Rupee about Christmas songs.
Hehe!
adviseScripts.speaker: Rupee

adviseScripts.text: I'm in a good mood today.
adviseScripts.speaker: Rupee

adviseScripts.text: I'm enjoying spending time with you too.
Did you get the coupons?
You really mean it?
adviseScripts.speaker: Rupee

adviseScripts.text: It's like you can read my mind!
adviseScripts.speaker: Rupee

adviseScripts.text: Sometimes...
adviseScripts.speaker: Rupee

adviseScripts.text: It feels like you think all I do is shopping.
adviseScripts.speaker: Rupee

adviseScripts.text: Which, of course, is totally right.
adviseScripts.speaker: Rupee

adviseScripts.text: I enjoy a fun time with the tension high Rupee.
Sweetie, which do I look better in?
adviseScripts.speaker: Rupee

adviseScripts.text: White or black?
adviseScripts.speaker: Rupee

adviseScripts.text: White, obviously.
I prefer black. It's sexier.
I think so too.
adviseScripts.speaker: Rupee

adviseScripts.text: I was buying my winter clothes, and I think I pull off white much better.
adviseScripts.speaker: Rupee

adviseScripts.text: Of course, I'm always open to trying black someday.
adviseScripts.speaker: Rupee

adviseScripts.text: Really?
adviseScripts.speaker: Rupee

adviseScripts.text: I mean, of course I'm all for sex appeal,
adviseScripts.speaker: Rupee

adviseScripts.text: but I don't think black is the way to go this winter.
adviseScripts.speaker: Rupee

adviseScripts.text: Rupee and I talk about what colors suit her best.
Sweetie, Sweetie!
adviseScripts.speaker: Rupee

adviseScripts.text: How old were you when you stopped believing in Santa Claus?
adviseScripts.speaker: Rupee

adviseScripts.text: I never stopped believing in Santa.
Santa... doesn't exist?
You're kidding.
adviseScripts.speaker: Rupee

adviseScripts.text: I always thought he wasn't real.
adviseScripts.speaker: Rupee

adviseScripts.text: Well, since you're such a believer, I may have to reconsider.
adviseScripts.speaker: Rupee

adviseScripts.text: Let's think about what presents we should ask him for this year.
adviseScripts.speaker: Rupee

adviseScripts.text: I'm sorry! I didn't know you actually believed in him...
adviseScripts.speaker: Rupee

adviseScripts.text: I have a debate with Rupee about Santa Claus' existence.
The year is nearly over.
adviseScripts.speaker: Rupee

adviseScripts.text: Do you have any vacation plans?
adviseScripts.speaker: Rupee

adviseScripts.text: I'm going to kick back and relax on my own.
None. Help me plan something.
Right... it's nice to have some time alone every once in a while.
adviseScripts.speaker: Rupee

adviseScripts.text: I'll do the same.
adviseScripts.speaker: Rupee

adviseScripts.text: Does that mean you could spend time with me?
adviseScripts.speaker: Rupee

adviseScripts.text: Sure.
You better be serious, because I am.
adviseScripts.speaker: Rupee

adviseScripts.text: I'll make this a vacation that you'll never forget.
adviseScripts.speaker: Rupee

adviseScripts.text: I spend time with Rupee while vacation planning.
The temperature has really gone down.
adviseScripts.speaker: Rupee

adviseScripts.text: I'm fine with it, but what about you? Aren't you freezing?
adviseScripts.speaker: Rupee

adviseScripts.text: I could use a few more layers, yeah.
It's okay. You can hold my hand.
Hehe, I knew this would happen, so I brought a coat just for you.
adviseScripts.speaker: Rupee

adviseScripts.text: Try it on.
adviseScripts.speaker: Rupee

adviseScripts.text: Do you really think that would work?
adviseScripts.speaker: Rupee

adviseScripts.text: Rupee gently takes my hand.
Actually, my hand feels a bit warmer now too.
adviseScripts.speaker: Rupee

adviseScripts.text: I spend a warm moment with Rupee.
It's really cold tonight. How about we go eat something that'll warm us up?
adviseScripts.speaker: Rupee

adviseScripts.text: I'm sure we'll be able to find something in the Ark.
adviseScripts.speaker: Rupee

adviseScripts.text: Let's just have some Ramen Splendamin.
I think a place just opened up that sells truffle soup.
You mean the stuff they sell at Talentum Mall?
adviseScripts.speaker: Rupee

adviseScripts.text: I've never tried it... but I'm willing to try if you come along.
adviseScripts.speaker: Rupee

adviseScripts.text: I've been wanting to go there for ages now!
adviseScripts.speaker: Rupee

adviseScripts.text: Apparently it's nearly indistinguishable from the real thing.
adviseScripts.speaker: Rupee

adviseScripts.text: Let's go right now!
adviseScripts.speaker: Rupee

adviseScripts.text: Rupee and I warm ourselves up with some tasty treats.
I may have gone overboard with the shopping lately. I'm a bit tired.
adviseScripts.speaker: Rupee

adviseScripts.text: *Yawn*
adviseScripts.speaker: Rupee

adviseScripts.text: How can shopping make you tired?
You can lean on my shoulder if you want.
Hehe, you saw right through me.
adviseScripts.speaker: Rupee

adviseScripts.text: To be honest, I just wanted to put my head on your shoulder.
adviseScripts.speaker: Rupee

adviseScripts.text: Rupee grabs my arm and pulls herself closer.
Ah... this is the stuff.
adviseScripts.speaker: Rupee

adviseScripts.text: Can I?
adviseScripts.speaker: Rupee

adviseScripts.text: Well... don't mind if I do!
adviseScripts.speaker: Rupee

adviseScripts.text: I spend some nice quiet time with Rupee.
Pop quiz!
adviseScripts.speaker: Rupee

adviseScripts.text: When do you find me most appealing?
adviseScripts.speaker: Rupee

adviseScripts.text: When you've just stepped out of the shower.
When you're out on a date.
Eww, you're creepy.
adviseScripts.speaker: Rupee

adviseScripts.text: But then again, that means you appreciate me in my natural state...
adviseScripts.speaker: Rupee

adviseScripts.text: All right, from now on I'll show that "side" of me more often.
adviseScripts.speaker: Rupee

adviseScripts.text: That's because I'm over the moon whenever I'm out with you, Sweetie!
adviseScripts.speaker: Rupee

adviseScripts.text: So that's when I'm at my best.
adviseScripts.speaker: Rupee

adviseScripts.text: I'm glad you noticed how happy you make me!
adviseScripts.speaker: Rupee

adviseScripts.text: I listen to Rupee as she tell me about how makeup can create different moods.
The last time it snowed in the Outpost,
adviseScripts.speaker: Rupee

adviseScripts.text: 30 couples got married.
adviseScripts.speaker: Rupee

adviseScripts.text: A wedding on a snowy day... Isn't it romantic?
adviseScripts.speaker: Rupee

adviseScripts.text: Would you like to rehearse?
Someday, we'll be able to see snow on the surface.
Rehearse? With who?
adviseScripts.speaker: Rupee

adviseScripts.text: With me.
I just imagined it...
adviseScripts.speaker: Rupee

adviseScripts.text: what a wonderful image.
adviseScripts.speaker: Rupee

adviseScripts.text: If anyone can do it, it's you, Sweetie.
adviseScripts.speaker: Rupee

adviseScripts.text: And I'll be there to help!
adviseScripts.speaker: Rupee

adviseScripts.text: I have a conversation with Rupee about our dream wedding.
I'm trying to have a New Year's party,
adviseScripts.speaker: Rupee

adviseScripts.text: but I'm not sure what kind of party it should be.
adviseScripts.speaker: Rupee

adviseScripts.text: A black tie event for celebrities and your clients.
A casual get-together with your fans and other livestreamers.
Are you sure?
adviseScripts.speaker: Rupee

adviseScripts.text: They are valuable clients, and it would help with future sales,
adviseScripts.speaker: Rupee

adviseScripts.text: but it'd also be so boring...
adviseScripts.speaker: Rupee

adviseScripts.text: I was thinking of something similar.
adviseScripts.speaker: Rupee

adviseScripts.text: The year is nearly over, so we should end it in style. I can have other streamers join my livestream.
adviseScripts.speaker: Rupee

adviseScripts.text: Of course, you and I will be the main highlight. Maybe we should do something like a couple's dance?
adviseScripts.speaker: Rupee

adviseScripts.text: I plan a New Year's party with Rupee.
I'm going through some rough times right now.
adviseScripts.speaker: Rupee

adviseScripts.text: It's the end of the year, and I have so many purchases to make, and all these documents to process...
adviseScripts.speaker: Rupee

adviseScripts.text: It's been days since my last livestream...
adviseScripts.speaker: Rupee

adviseScripts.text: It's tough being the one in charge.
I know it's hard. Let me give you a massage.
I never envisioned myself in this line of work.
adviseScripts.speaker: Rupee

adviseScripts.text: Wouldn't it be nice if we could just do the things that we enjoy?
adviseScripts.speaker: Rupee

adviseScripts.text: Hehe, thanks!
adviseScripts.speaker: Rupee

adviseScripts.text: It'll be nice to take a load off.
adviseScripts.speaker: Rupee

adviseScripts.text: I console Rupee, who has been swamped with paperwork.
Our mall is preparing a year-end sale.
adviseScripts.speaker: Rupee

adviseScripts.text: What catchphrase should we use to hook people in?
adviseScripts.speaker: Rupee

adviseScripts.text: May your Christmas be a luxurious one. All high-end products are on sale.
Get the latest holiday fashions for you and your loved ones.
Not bad, but it's a little wordy.
adviseScripts.speaker: Rupee

adviseScripts.text: I'll think it over. If I can't come up with anything else, I'll go with your suggestion.
adviseScripts.speaker: Rupee

adviseScripts.text: Thanks, Sweetie.
adviseScripts.speaker: Rupee

adviseScripts.text: A lot of people who watch my channel have significant others, so that could really appeal to them!
adviseScripts.speaker: Rupee

adviseScripts.text: Oooh! You could also dress up for a photo shoot,
adviseScripts.speaker: Rupee

adviseScripts.text: and I could use it for advertising!
adviseScripts.speaker: Rupee

adviseScripts.text: Me?
Of course! I wouldn't want anybody else.
adviseScripts.speaker: Rupee

adviseScripts.text: It'd also be my way of showing you off, hehe.
adviseScripts.speaker: Rupee

adviseScripts.text: Rupee and I continue to brainstorm ideas.
